---
title: Greek-Style Haloumi & Oregano Wedges with Radish Salad & Garlic Yoghurt
description: There are plenty of surprises in this meal. With honey and dried oregano coating the haloumi you get herby, gooey, squeaky
sweetness, while the radish salad gives a sharp contrast. You’ll be wishing you could have this every night!
